---
title: Mediterranean Roasted Veggie Sandwich with Lemony Feta and Arugula Salad
description: Embrace your Mediterranean side with this patio-ready roasted veggie sandwich, layered with lots of flavourful trimmings!  A lemony feta and arugula salad brings an extra hit of sunshine.
